        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2487789626" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16195403210561394667">&quot;I am happy to have found here an elderly man with some dignity, and a young lady who knows how to be silent&quot;.<br/><br/>A touching story and beautiful story that shows the effects of war on a human level. <br/><br/>I wish I knew French so I could read it in the original language!<br/><br/><img src='https://images.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1535200510ra/26196752.gif' width='300' height='300' alt='description&quot;/' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/> <br/><br/><img src='https://images.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1535200510ra/26196753.gif' width='300' height='300' alt='description&quot;/' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/> <br/><br/><img src='https://images.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1535200510ra/26196751.gif' width='300' height='300' alt='description&quot;/' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/></span>
  <span id="freeText16195403210561394667" style="display:none">"I am happy to have found here an elderly man with some dignity, and a young lady who knows how to be silent".<br><br>A touching story and beautiful story that shows the effects of war on a human level. <br><br>I wish I knew French so I could read it in the original language!<br><br><img src="https://images.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1535200510ra/26196752.gif" width="300" height="300" alt='description"/' class="gr-hostedUserImg"> <br><br><img src="https://images.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1535200510ra/26196753.gif" width="300" height="300" alt='description"/' class="gr-hostedUserImg"> <br><br><img src="https://images.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1535200510ra/26196751.gif" width="300" height="300" alt='description"/' class="gr-hostedUserImg"></span>
