        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1822360683" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5315190227154222038">Read the English translation (or Chinese?...or both) and watched the movie. <br/><br/>This one is among my top five war (of all time) stories. Almost all of them are about the collision and doomed mutual affection of individuals epitomizing the culture/civilization of his/her own country/class in the context of a major war. <br/><br/><br/></span>

          </span>
        </div>


